{
    "content":{
        "from":"features@sparkpostbox.com",
        "html":"<html>
  <body>
    <h1>SparkPost Email Template Features</h1>
    <p>Insert substitution variables: I like {{flavor}} ice cream.</p>
    <p>Make some content conditional: Your ice cream is {{if flavor == "strawberry"}} pink {{else}} cream{{end}}-colored.</p>
    <p>Iterate through items in a list:
      <ul>
        {{each desserts}}
        <li>{{loop_var}}</li>
        {{end}}
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p>Inserting HTML using variables:
      {{{setMenuHTML}}}
    </p>
    <p>Inserting HTML containing variables:
      {{render_dynamic_content(dynamic_html.setMenuHTMLWithSpecial)}}
    </p>
    <p>Controlling links:
      <ul>
        <li>Named links for reporting: <a data-msys-linkname="SparkPost" href="https://www.sparkpost.com/">SparkPost</a></li>
        <li>Labelling an unsubscribe linke: <a data=msys-unsubscribe="1" href="http://www.example.com/unsubs">unsubscribe</a></li>
        <li>Controlling link tracking for a single link: <a data-msys-clicktrack="0" href="https://www.example.com/">don't track this</a></li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
",
        "subject":"features",
        "text":"SparkPost Email Template Features

Insert substitution variables: I like {{flavor}} ice cream.

Make some content conditional: Your ice cream is {{if flavor == "strawberry"}} pink {{else}} cream{{end}}-colored.

Iterate through items in a list:
{{each desserts}}
- {{loop_var}}
{{end}}

Inserting text using variables:
{{{setMenuText}}}

Inserting text containing variables:
{{render_dynamic_content(dynamic_plain.setMenuTextWithSpecial)}}

Controlling links:
- Named links for reporting: https://www.sparkpost.com/[[data-msys-linkname="SparkPost"]]

- Labelling an unsubscribe linke: http://www.example.com/unsubs[[data=msys-unsubscribe="1"]]

- Controlling link tracking for a single link: https://www.example.com/[[data-msys-clicktrack="0"]]

"
    },
    "description":"Send email using template: features",
    "recipients":[
        {
            "address":"you@example.sinkhole.sparkpostmail.com"
        }
    ],
    "substitution_data":{
        "desserts":[
            "ice cream",
            "profiteroles",
            "blancmange",
            "bread pudding"
        ],
        "dynamic_html":{
            "setMenuHTMLWithSpecial":"<ol><li><b>Special: {{specialDish}}</b></li><li>Soup</li><li>Steak frites</li><li>Ice cream</li></ol>"
        },
        "dynamic_plain":{
            "setMenuTextWithSpecial":"Special: {{specialDish}}
Soup, Steak frites and Ice cream"
        },
        "flavor":"chocolate",
        "setMenuHTML":"<ol><li><b>Soup</b></li><li>Steak frites</li><li>Ice cream</li></ol>",
        "setMenuText":"-Soup
-Steak frites
-Ice cream",
        "specialDish":"Tête de veau"
    }
}

{
    "content":{
        "from":"pref-driven@sparkpostbox.com",
        "html":"<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">

<title>Your News Digest</title>

<style type="text/css">
  /* Outlook/live.com fixes */
	.ReadMsgBody {width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff;}
	.ExternalClass {width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff;}

	body	 {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    font-family: Georgia, Times, serif
  }

	table { border-collapse: collapse; }

	@media only screen and (max-width: 640px)  {
					.deviceWidth {
            width: 440px !important;
            padding: 0;
          }
					.center { text-align: center !important; }
          .header { padding: 0 0 10px 0 !important; }
			}

	@media only screen and (max-width: 479px) {
					.deviceWidth {
            width: 280px !important;
            padding: 0;
          }
					.center { text-align: center !important; }
          .header { padding: 0 0 10px 0 !important; }
			}
</style>
</head>

<body leftmargin="0" topmargin="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" style="font-family: Georgia, Times, serif">

<table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center">
	<tbody><tr>
		<td width="100%" valign="top">

			<table width="580" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" class="deviceWidth" style="margin:0 auto;">
				<tbody><tr>
					<td width="100%">

              <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="left" class="deviceWidth">
                  <tbody><tr>
                      <td class="header center" style="padding:25px 0px" class="center">
                          <a href="#"><img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/avocado-logo-sml.png" alt="" border="0"></a>
                      </td>
                  </tr>
              </tbody></table>

              <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="right" class="deviceWidth">
                  <tbody><tr>
                      <td class="header center" style="text-align: right; vertical-align: middle; padding:30px 0px;">
                        <a href="#"><img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/twitter.png" alt="" border="0"></a>
                        <a href="#"><img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/facebook.png" alt="" border="0"></a>
                        <a href="#"><img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/instagram.png" alt="" border="0"></a>
                        <a href="#"><img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/gplus.png" alt="" border="0"></a>
                        <a href="#"><img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/github.png" alt="" border="0"></a>
                      </td>
                  </tr>
              </tbody></table>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody></table>


{{each recip_prefs}}

			<table width="580" class="deviceWidth" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" style="margin:0 auto;">
          <tbody><tr>
              <td class="header" style="font-size: 32px; color: #54565A; font-weight: normal; text-align: center; font-family: Georgia, Times, serif; vertical-align: top; padding:60px 0px 30px 0px">
                {{loop_var.name}}
              </td>
          </tr>
			</tbody></table>

			<table width="580" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" class="deviceWidth" style="margin:0 auto;">
				<tbody><tr>
					<td class="center" style="padding:35px 40px 0px 40px">
  {{each loop_var.ids}}

              <table width="49%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="left" class="deviceWidth">
                  <tbody><tr>
                      <td align="center">
                        <!-- The paragraph tag is important here to ensure that this table floats properly in Outlook 2007, 2010, and 2013
                          To learn more about this fix check out this link: https://www.emailonacid.com/blog/details/C13/removing_unwanted_spacing_or_gaps_between_tables_in_outlook_2007_2010
                          This fix is used for all floating tables in this responsive template
                          The margin set to 0 is for Gmail -->
                          <p style="mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0; margin:0">
                            <a href="#">
                              <img width="235" src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/2upimg.png" alt="" border="0" class="deviceWidth">
                            </a>
                          </p>
                      </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                      <td style="font-size: 12px; color: #54565A; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; font-family: Georgia, Times, serif; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px 8px 0px 8px">
                        <a href="#" style="text-decoration: none; font-size: 20px; color: #54565A; font-weight: normal; font-family:Georgia, Times, serif">{{articles[loop_var].headline}}</a>
                        <p>{{articles[loop_var].content}}</p>
                      </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:0px 8px 10px 8px">
                      <a style="color: #76c7ff; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-decoration: none" href="{{render_dynamic_content(dynamic_html[loop_var])}}">Learn more</a>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
              </tbody></table>

  {{end}}
{{end}}

              <table><tbody><tr><td class="header" style="padding: 50px"></td></tr></tbody></table>

              <table background="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/footer-bg.jpg" width="100%">
                <tbody><tr>
                  <td style="text-align: center; padding: 40px 0 0 0">
                    <img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/white-avocado-logo-sml.png" alt="" />
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-size: 50px; font-family: Georgia, Times, serif; color: #FFFFFF; text-align: center; padding: 5px 0 0 0">
                    Growing Quality.
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #FFFFFF; text-align: center; padding: 15px 0 15px 0">
                    Avocado Industries, 1200 Farmers Way, Jacksonville, FL 20202<br/>
                    &copy; 2017 Avocado Industries. All rights reserved.
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="center" style="text-align: center">
                      <a href="#"><img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/twitter.png" alt="" border="0"></a>
                      <a href="#"><img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/facebook.png" alt="" border="0"></a>
                      <a href="#"><img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/instagram.png" alt="" border="0"></a>
                      <a href="#"><img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/gplus.png" alt="" border="0"></a>
                      <a href="#"><img src="https://sparkpost.github.io/template-library/templates/assets/github.png" alt="" border="0"></a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <table width="80%" align="center">
                      <tbody><tr>
                        <td align="left"><a style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif" href="#">Privacy Policy</a></td>
                        <td align="center"><a style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif" href="#">Update email</a></td>
                        <td align="right"><a style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif" href="#">Unsubscribe</a></td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding-bottom: 40px" colspan="3"></td>
                      </tr></tbody>
                    </table>
                </tr></tbody>
              </table>

					</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody></table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</tbody></table>
</body></html>
",
        "subject":"pref-driven",
        "text":"{{each recip_prefs}}
**{{loop_var.name}}**

{{each loop_var.ids}}
*{{articles[loop_var].headline}}*
{{articles[loop_var].content}}
{{articles[loop_var].url}}

{{end}}
{{end}}
"
    },
    "description":"Send email using template: pref-driven",
    "recipients":[
        {
            "address":"you@example.sinkhole.sparkpostmail.com"
        }
    ],
    "substitution_data":{
